    "description": "<strong>《PAPERHEAD》“EP.0”</strong>包含<strong>快节奏移动、轰炸枪击</strong>以及<strong>恐怖剧情</strong>，并辅以<strong>独特的配乐</strong>。<br><br>在“EP.0”（第0章）中，你在牢房中醒来，听见一个古怪的声音在布满符文与鲜血的黑暗走廊深处呼唤自己。给可靠的霰弹枪装好子弹，启程寻找真相。<br><i><strong>……纸板人为什么会……流血？</strong></i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>雷厉风行的残酷激战</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>抛掷敌人，瞄准它们踢出火药桶，然后像某个意大利水管工一样迎头跳下！<br></li><li>或者简单点，直接用霰弹枪轰碎它们！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008200/extras/0618d673f9f7ec3ba0945155bae5e012.poster.avif?t=1761924664\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008200/extras/0618d673f9f7ec3ba0945155bae5e012.webm?t=1761924664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008200/extras/0618d673f9f7ec3ba0945155bae5e012.mp4?t=1761924664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>画出道路，逃离<i>[已删除]</i></strong></h2>铅笔——是武器，也是改变周遭世界的工具。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>画出炸弹，踢向敌人！<br></li><li>画出门板，一脚踢翻！<br></li><li>在墙上书写 ██████ 字句——干就完了！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008200/extras/346fbf5a6b4bc08f654598504ab3e635.poster.avif?t=1761924664\" width=640 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008200/extras/346fbf5a6b4bc08f654598504ab3e635.webm?t=1761924664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008200/extras/346fbf5a6b4bc08f654598504ab3e635.mp4?t=1761924664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可爱……但也可怕</strong></h2>可爱迷人的纸板世界，比想象中更加有血有肉。纸片也能让人毛骨悚然！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008200/extras/f88db1b8826314b7745f9b5848e88c65.poster.avif?t=1761924664\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008200/extras/f88db1b8826314b7745f9b5848e88c65.webm?t=1761924664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008200/extras/f88db1b8826314b7745f9b5848e88c65.mp4?t=1761924664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>纸片有时比金属更坚韧</strong></h2>工业风配乐，营造一触即发的激情。<br><br>大步向前，探明真相……<br><strong>纸板人为什么会……流血？</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008200/extras/12ca7346667269776e717fce130c03c3.poster.avif?t=1761924664\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008200/extras/12ca7346667269776e717fce130c03c3.webm?t=1761924664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008200/extras/12ca7346667269776e717fce130c03c3.mp4?t=1761924664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>P.S. 小心！游戏时不要割伤手指 :-)",
